# ===========================================
# Python Edition Frontend — Environment Variables
# ===========================================
# Vite bakes these at BUILD time (important for Render static sites).

# --- LOCAL (default: Vite proxy to localhost:5000) ---
# Leave unset or comment out to use /api proxy from vite.config.ts

# VITE_API_BASE_URL=/api

# --- PRODUCTION (Render static site) ---
# Set in Render → Static Site → Environment BEFORE deploy/build
# Example (replace with your API service URL):
# VITE_API_BASE_URL=https://python-edition-api.onrender.com/api

# --- NOT USED ---
# VITE_SUPABASE_URL — obsolete (app uses MongoDB + JWT via Express)
# VITE_SUPABASE_ANON_KEY — obsolete
